http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#lab.value: List of war films and TV specials set between 1945 and 2001

http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#com.value: War depictions in film and television include documentaries, TV mini-series, and drama serials depicting aspects of historical wars. The films included here are set in the time period from 1945 to 2001, or from the start of the Cold War until it came to an end in 1990s. The Cold War itself was the aftermath of World War II. At the turn of the new century the world woke up to a new reality one September morning and Cold War's aftermath period came to an end.
